Node "Ferd_3_2b_1"
notes ""
{
NPCText "*He frowns and snorts with frustration.* Maybe a few years ago, before we found all there was to find around Crossroads, yes, there were big amounts of caps to be made."
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "- MORE -" linkto "Ferd_3_2b_2"  notes ""
              }
}
Node "Ferd_3_2b_2"
notes ""
{
NPCText "These days? When it is really quiet, some of us even work as guards for the caravans. I don' know if there is much left to be explored aroun' here."
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "If it came to it, could you become a caravan guard permanently?" linkto "Ferd_3_2b_3"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "What job do you have with the Wasteland Explorers?" linkto "Ferd_3_1b_1"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Excuse me, I have to go." linkto "done"  notes ""
              }
}
Node "Ferd_3_2b_3"
notes ""
{
NPCText "Si, I could do that. But I don' wan' to. This life... it is good, you know? I would rather be exploring the world rather than just travelling back an' forward between the same towns."
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "I do a lot of travelling. Would you like to come with me?" linkto "Ferd_0"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "May I ask you a question about something else?" linkto "Ferd_9"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Excuse me, I have to go." linkto "done"  notes ""
              }
}
Node "Ferd_9"
notes ""
{
